ignificant experience in activist investing in north america and was seeded by grosvenor capital management lp one of the oldest and largest global alternative investment managers engaged capital is a limited liability company owned by its principals and formed to create longterm shareholder value by bringing an owner’s perspective to the managements and boards of undervalued public companies engaged capital’s efforts and resources are dedicated to a single investment style “constructive activism” with a focus on delivering superior longterm riskadjusted returns for investors engaged capital is based in newport beach california contacts media contactbayfield strategy incriyaz lalani  rlalanibayfieldstrategycom release summary engaged capital issues statement in respect of rentacenter contacts media contactbayfield strategy incriyaz lalani  rlalanibayfieldstrategycom search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up ﻿ engaged capital llc purchases shares of  the hain celestial group inc nasdaqhain  bnb daily daily ratings  news for the hain celestial group inc complete the form below to receive the latest headlines and analysts recommendationsfor the hain celestial group inc with our free daily email newsletter follow bnbdailynews recent posts engaged capital llc purchases shares of  the hain celestial group inc nasdaqhain nrg energy target of unusually high options trading nysenrg navigator holdings ltd nysenvgs downgraded by zacks investment research new gold inc nysengd sees large growth in short interest independence realty trust inc nyseirt short interest update q  earnings forecast for lincoln national corporation nyselnc issued by langen mcalenn fortinet inc nasdaqftnt upgraded to positive at otr global st suffiel financ com nysefsff stock rating lowered by maxim group ulta beauty inc nasdaqulta earns market perform rating from wells fargo  company towne bank town rating increased to buy at zacks investment research the ultimate software group’s 